" 模拟 Emacs 键绑定
 " Move
 inoremap <C-a> <Home>
 inoremap <C-e> <End>
 inoremap <C-p> <Up>
 inoremap <C-n> <Down>
 inoremap <C-b> <Left>
 inoremap <C-f> <Right>
 inoremap <M-b> <C-o>b
 inoremap <M-f> <C-o>w
 " Rubout word / line and enter insert mode
 " use <Esc><Right> instead of <C-o>
 inoremap <C-w> <Esc>dbcl
 " delete
 inoremap <C-u> <Esc>d0cl
 inoremap <C-k> <Esc><Right>C
 inoremap <C-d> <Esc><Right>s
 inoremap <M-d> <C-o>de
